Package: adaptiveFTS
Title: Adaptive Functional Time Series Analysis
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R:
    person("Hassan", "Maissoro", , "maissorohassan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description:
  Adaptive estimation procedures for weakly dependent functional time series,
  following Maissoro, Patilea and Vimond (2024) and (2025). Provides estimators
  for the local regularity parameters, the mean function, and the autocovariance
  function, together with an adaptive estimator of the Best Linear Unbiased
  Predictor (BLUP) for prediction.
